{"tid":482982,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）煎牛扒分享","createTime":"2017-11-28T16:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T12:52:11.000Z","uid":68044,"like":66,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4b47585b3270dbca1def00b8c08bb04be06da2cb","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"每個人煎扒都有自己既方法同心得，<br />\n尋日用左少場時間整理下自己覺得重要既幾點。<br />\n<br />\nVideo  : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fatcookpage/videos/951499241674798/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffatcookpage%2Fvideos%2F951499241674798%2F&d=DstuGdSe1pRyRRMD08SOs0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4015c078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fatcookpage/videos/951499241674798/</a><br />\n<br />\n最重要幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1）煎之前最少10分鐘攞出嚟放喺室溫。<br />\n<br />\n2）印乾表面，會影響個browning 做得好唔好同令肉入面overcooked。<br />\n<br />\n3）煮之前一刻先落鹽，唔好落完鹽走左去轉頭先返黎煎，原因係鹽會抽走肉既水分。（除非你早一個鐘以上落鹽）<br />\n<br />\n4）Hot pan，依個最難講解，唔會愈熱愈好，因為有機會燒窿咗表面入邊都仲係凍。總括就係適當地熱，只少你聽到煎野d 聲，同我煎既時間都係有煙的。<br />\n<br />\n5）煎完要rest，唔好切，一切就前功盡棄，咩juice 都流哂出黎，等只少五分鐘，你唔心急既用錫紙cover 10-15 分鐘仲好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係最重要既重要：<br />\n<br />\n6）買扒既時間唔好買薄扒，我鐘意用兩隻手指咁厚既扒。薄既唔洗講咩medium，你brown 得黎都變牛肉乾。<br />\n<br />\n7）煎到一半嘅時候，我加左牛油thyme rosemary garlic (optional)，成程係咁淋嚮個扒既面，你試過就會知出黎個味有分別。<br />\n<br />\n想再了解睇埋d 理論：<br />\n<br />\n煎扒既目標有三個：<br />\n<br />\n1）外層有好靚既深啡色。依個browning 既過程叫 Maillard reaction，過程中會釋放好多種唔同既香味。（唔明既試下諗下白灼同煎既分別）<br />\n<br />\n2）煮到一個剛剛好既煮度。蛋白質愈熱會愈收縮，過程中會擠出肉入面既水份。<br />\n簡單講，全熟既肉係會乾的。<br />\n要一塊juicy 既肉，煮度就無比重要。<br />\n咁點知塊扒幾煮？可以用溫度計，不過扒既話我唔建議，因為太薄，唔太準；個人會用手感覺，越熟嘅扒會愈實。<br />\n<br />\n咁我自己就鐘意 medium rare 既，個人意見係任何超過medium 都開始乾的。<br />\n<br />\nRemarks, 溫度同煮度既關係<br />\nRare               - 49c<br />\nMedium rare - 54c<br />\nMedium         - 59c<br />\n<br />\n3) 嚮browning 既表面同中心之間over cooked 既範圍減到最少。<br />\n<br />\n講多兩個煎牛排既迷思：<br />\n<br />\n1）brown 左個表面可以鎖住d 肉汁 - 係樣野係唔存在的。<br />\n<br />\n任何food science 既書都會咁講，乾同唔乾最主要係因為有無overcook，蛋白質收縮嘅關係，同有無Brown 係無關係的。<br />\n諗下最多汁既煮法係sous vide，都無Brown 過就煮。<br />\n<br />\n2）煎既時候只可反一次or 唔好成日反。<br />\n<br />\nWhy ???<br />\n<br />\nFat Duck 既 Heston Blumenthal (Michelin 3 stars) 既方法係每15秒-20秒反一次。<br />\n（最睇既去Youtube search How to cook like Heston - beef)<br />\n<br />\n另外我睇過個test 測試唔同時間反牛扒既效果，都係15 秒反一次既效果最好。<br />\n不過個人覺得自己煮又唔洗咁精準，總之唔好比&rsquo;&lsquo;只可以反一次&lsquo;&rsquo;嚇親自己。"},{"pid":"47d906a36fbc74fe051e6bf418d32e919a9e4469","tid":482982,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"等睇潮文"},{"pid":"acac68d554d1685f8a38e51ab5c523e846842cb0","tid":482982,"uid":122634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854e712fad7e02e16746dc81e0279ab9220dbbc6","tid":482982,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372f10275efa38a773b67280bd7f0ddedea55b84","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嚮倫敦d 肉檔買😅<br />\n香港既可以去銅鑼灣近跑馬地響麥當勞對面嘅凍肉鋪買，都ok"},{"pid":"e3394e4de699c16c78caddc95a522d3e1155b0d8","tid":482982,"uid":8203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"如果得塊薄野點煎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有無食開邊個產地"},{"pid":"24a4d6e37c30a2971d4cb49a3b3bf987162c9bc0","tid":482982,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"2）印乾表面，會影響個browning 做得好唔好同令肉入面overcooked。<br />\n<br />\n即係印唔印好？"},{"pid":"258e29ac7235fbf008a3a50af789d9359687c947","tid":482982,"uid":6044,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:35:03.000Z","msg":"迷思1<br />\n<br />\n我覺得蕉左（黑色）應該可以防止有肉汁流出黎<br />\n原理就好似受傷你結在蕉就唔會有野流出黎<br />\n不過前提係成隻蕉晒先得<br />\n你見美國佬bbq成日燒到成舊炭咁先去焗就係咁解<br />\n不過針無兩頭利，應該好苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我諗你講應該係深啡色<br />\n我自己覺得顏色代表香口度<br />\n要鎖肉汁除非蕉左即係黑色<br />\n如果唔係無咩大分別<br />\n要有肉汁最緊要煎個時夠熱同有reset<br />\n<br />\n迷思2<br />\n<br />\n一定唔係只可反一次<br />\n唔好成日反其實啱<br />\n如果你係咁反佢，佢會係咁出血水<br />\n比時間去煮先能夠把熱力傳入去<br />\n你自己用15s<br />\n我自己覺得應該睇pan熱度同埋你會點煮去決定<br />\n只係煎定煎完入爐焗<br />\n出面師傅煎開扒話唔好成日返<br />\n係因為佢要有靚嘅十字紋（grill mark）比人睇<br />\n所以每邊煎2次先會咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋扒房煎個d唔係用pan<br />\n所以唔會煎個時落牛油，蒜頭同其他香草<br />\n只係有鹽同黑椒<br />\n你叫佢煎香d，其實心裡覺得你on9<br />\n唔會有分別<br />\n有d西餐廳會係葉個時落香草同蒜片<br />\n不過唔多"},{"pid":"ebefc98bc4d17a7deb7d06dcedee217a01ac671e","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2）印乾表面，會影響個browning 做得好唔好同令肉入面overcooked。<br />\n<br />\n即係印唔印好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry, 1999.<br />\n係要印乾個面，唔係既話要長啲時間先brown 到，咁入面會大d 機會overcook"},{"pid":"ba259c078d89b6986b2a5aee4f331a1ea30ddfad","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果得塊薄野點煎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有無食開邊個產地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己會用好大好大火，希望做到表面Brown 入面唔好太overcook"},{"pid":"82f037116159bd0ec7e6541615575ef2d0d6740d","tid":482982,"uid":13541,"like":25,"dislike":8,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:42:58.000Z","msg":"其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以甘樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦"},{"pid":"662bbbf08d8745d30bf6c6e5201d294986200676","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:43:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果得塊薄野點煎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有無食開邊個產地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己會用好大好大火，希望做到表面Brown 入面唔好太overcook</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n產地就無研究，唔敢拍專家"},{"pid":"dec07889a41b410814cfe46f75d2d864880ee536","tid":482982,"uid":78222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:48:43.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講下你個扒總供煎左幾耐反左幾次 <br />\n同埋想知幾時煎側邊同煎幾耐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己唔太識煮 唔知係咪太大火關係 有陣時出面已經啡色 但係入面未熟透  搞到煎完再焗爐輔助 但係又變得熟過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變左七成"},{"pid":"30da678df3dc8c0297b5b2e633ff11aa04768a88","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以講下你個扒總供煎左幾耐反左幾次 <br />\n同埋想知幾時煎側邊同煎幾耐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己唔太識煮 唔知係咪太大火關係 有陣時出面已經啡色 但係入面未熟透  搞到煎完再焗爐輔助 但係又變得熟過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變左七成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你煎完再焗依個方法係無問題，我自己又或者專業廚師煮好多時都會係咁。<br />\n<br />\n我自己無數反幾多次，除非你煎塊扒次次嘅size 都一樣，唔係嘅話時間都有出入，我自己就嘗試用手去撳下塊扒睇有幾實，我覺得咁樣長線比較準。"},{"pid":"20a7f40b9607289c62237cac969e80f66109219a","tid":482982,"uid":6044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以講下你個扒總供煎左幾耐反左幾次 <br />\n同埋想知幾時煎側邊同煎幾耐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己唔太識煮 唔知係咪太大火關係 有陣時出面已經啡色 但係入面未熟透  搞到煎完再焗爐輔助 但係又變得熟過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變左七成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己如果用pan就煎左邊先之後先煎面<br />\n你自己識講太大火<br />\n校細d試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果想快d去到medium又唔想入焗爐<br />\n可以用馬碟cup住塊扒<br />\n變成半煎焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果面reset就煎低一個成數<br />\n要食medium就煎rare medium"},{"pid":"96bb8b9ac1243867061947f5f3fb421a75fb6edf","tid":482982,"uid":6044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打可唔可以講下你個扒總供煎左幾耐反左幾次 <br />\n同埋想知幾時煎側邊同煎幾耐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己唔太識煮 唔知係咪太大火關係 有陣時出面已經啡色 但係入面未熟透  搞到煎完再焗爐輔助 但係又變得熟過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變左七成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己如果用pan就煎左邊先之後先煎面<br />\n你自己識講太大火<br />\n校細d試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果想快d去到medium又唔想入焗爐<br />\n可以用馬碟cup住塊扒<br />\n變成半煎焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">要</span>reset就煎低一個成數<br />\n要食medium就煎rare medium</blockquote>"},{"pid":"25db81501c99b034fb1de848d6fcbbde268b11c7","tid":482982,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T20:01:17.000Z","msg":"煎過10次左右  放棄左<br />\n一係就出面啡入面唔熟<br />\n一係就全熟 太硬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實買應該買幾錢既扒來試好？<br />\n岩岩開始   係market place 買D 40蚊一塊煎  次次都炒曬飛機"},{"pid":"f8938a66e3e9b98d9294371a2d0da655de59889d","tid":482982,"uid":22856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T20:09:30.000Z","msg":"難得一見糕汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮"},{"pid":"e79bdacc3849a0386980c6b35496fab7b736bed9","tid":482982,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T20:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煎過10次左右  放棄左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一係就出面啡入面唔熟</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一係就全熟 太硬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實買應該買幾錢既扒來試好？<br />\n岩岩開始   係market place 買D 40蚊一塊煎  次次都炒曬飛機</