et place佢用g去計幾錢<br />\n佢通常切左包到靚靚貼價錢<br />\n最少都2百左右<br />\n你40蚊個d戈係bbq牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啊師兄頭幾次煮邊有信心買咁貴<br />\n我未rich 到頭幾次就用過百蚊來試   <br />\n同埋你唔講我都唔知BBQ 牛扒原來40蚊咁平</blockquote><br />\n我唔知你40蚊係邊種<br />\n不過呢個價應該係大陸牛<br />\n但有d牛排係唔適合拿黎練<br />\n由其佢係凍肉櫃一包幾十有幾塊個d<br />\n（發泡膠底用保鮮紙包着）<br />\n或姐連骨牛排<br />\n最主要原因係你唔知邊個部位切出黎<br />\n同埋有d好薄<br />\n咁你會控制唔到成數<br />\n好易overcook<br />\n<br />\n如果想平練<br />\n買first choose個牌子<br />\n佢pack好晒<br />\n不過肉質真係麻麻<br />\n但練習應該唔錯<br />\n價錢應該係80-100左右<br />\n我好耐沒買過了<br />\n唔知有沒加價"},{"pid":"a8c033fcbc8154de8a664f7b640f15c4085b1a28","tid":482982,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d91231049760c9cc5f04fc65ed994350066c11","tid":482982,"uid":6044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你教整壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9d5f5318b973f3eba623de99b73cbc500a48ae","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，<br />\n有諗過出條片講下炒蛋，雖然9萬人講過"},{"pid":"5e51f3f5d54fed45d654b7d37a1aec084c769fc2","tid":482982,"uid":148443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T22:05:10.000Z","msg":"好似翻譯Ramsay啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61b484004894bb7621c275b7b93a39458a37ac4","tid":482982,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T22:32:48.000Z","msg":"如果用焗爐玩溫度<br />\n早8度F 好拎出尼<br />\n拎左出尼佢個心仲會升多幾度"},{"pid":"41668e1f5e72c3780dc292bcff12fd9ec4d2cdd6","tid":482982,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T22:57:45.000Z","msg":"落鹽抽水唔好咩，冇水先肉味濃喎同 dry aged 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df9c5e60814731e5e8c7ddf0fd05dd7440c03c","tid":482982,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:29:34.000Z","msg":"人地外國高級餐廳煮嘅welldone係juicy 架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c025468839a72aec581f64fab808699ef75d5","tid":482982,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去一田買啲八十錢一百蚊個啲， 大火煎就已經好好食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 性價比高"},{"pid":"f2efeb5a7a9425d62ec7d66fd337d97ff57f14cd","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似翻譯Ramsay啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有佢講過既野都唔出奇，我好鐘意睇佢d 野<br />\n睇睇下唔多唔少學埋落嚮自己身上都唔覺。"},{"pid":"ede38b6901f509d29115b7fe2ae6fb12dd9f049f","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落鹽抽水唔好咩，冇水先肉味濃喎同 dry aged 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下分析下<br />\n<br />\nDry aged 肉味濃既原因係 enzymatic, bacterial action, 脂肪 oxidation 等等既過程產生左 beefy or 好似芝士咁既味。<br />\n<br />\n另外肉入面既enzyme 會breakdown 左肉既組織，令肉食落去淋d。<br />\n<br />\n落鹽抽水就少左上面兩個效果。"},{"pid":"070f14ca19dcf2fdc549032396a8ba56bb0424f4","tid":482982,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，<br />\n有諗過出條片講下炒蛋，雖然9萬人講過</blockquote><br />\n好高難度喎炒蛋"},{"pid":"15920ee3e0bc72e4025203f72f400fd613345a56","tid":482982,"uid":22175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，<br />\n有諗過出條片講下炒蛋，雖然9萬人講過</blockquote><br />\n好高難度喎炒蛋</blockquote><br />\n蛋真係易學難精 炒蛋其實係咪要加糖同牛奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da38aea4cbc53483c7194d46cf164955e41398f2","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地外國高級餐廳煮嘅welldone係juicy 架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心想試下，不過要比錢食well done steak 我過唔到自己...<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The amount of liquid water expelled from muscle fibers is related primarily to the temperature the meat is heated to. Meat that is cooked above 160F can become dry as water from the meat is release<br />\n<br />\nCollagen begins to denature at 140&deg;F/60&deg;C squeezing meat fibers leading to a release of juices (containing water) and shrinkage.<br />\n<br />\nAt 160F collagen will begin to dissolve and turn into a rich liquid, gelatin. This will give meat flavor and a silky texture.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nFrom <a href=\"http://www.scienceofcooking.com/why_does_meat_shrink_when_cooked.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scienceofcooking.com%2Fwhy_does_meat_shrink_when_cooked.htm&d=DstuGdSe1pRyRRMD08SOs0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3b0f14b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.scienceofcooking.com/why_does_meat_shrink_when_cooked.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b4e1343e5d60fd809a79f7a968d300cf3d42b547","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，<br />\n有諗過出條片講下炒蛋，雖然9萬人講過</blockquote><br />\n好高難度喎炒蛋</blockquote><br />\n蛋真係易學難精 炒蛋其實係咪要加糖同牛奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時試試，希望用到d 比較易明既方便分享下"},{"pid":"3f10e861df73862beb930e8016c0a4a8901ada7a","tid":482982,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:49:14.000Z","msg":"煎牛扒最緊要JAR JAR聲"},{"pid":"1cc5bfe73099a94efabf177e75f8b4ba9deb88ed","tid":482982,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落鹽抽水唔好咩，冇水先肉味濃喎同 dry aged 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下分析下<br />\n<br />\nDry aged 肉味濃既原因係 enzymatic, bacterial action, 脂肪 oxidation 等等既過程產生左 beefy or 好似芝士咁既味。<br />\n<br />\n另外肉入面既enzyme 會breakdown 左肉既組織，令肉食落去淋d。<br />\n<br />\n落鹽抽水就少左上面兩個效果。</blockquote><br />\n你啱Dry aged 唔止淨係抽水，不過抽水本身應該冇壞，尤其塊扒cheap"},{"pid":"c990dc8c522dec89c0cdcff027542945948a59ba","tid":482982,"uid":9975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c551ef8b21dfcf32fb5e565c5ae3152c99bd886d","tid":482982,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你教整壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食就識少少"},{"pid":"f6878e8f34c973978ff9573e414be1ce8d30908b","tid":482982,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ching 不如教其他野<br />\n係連登煎睇牛扒睇到好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，<br />\n有諗過出條片講下炒蛋，雖然9萬人講過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無啲難啲"},{"pid":"7d578f5712eb2778500952860186706a1e191e47","tid":482982,"uid":106856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"舊牛扒係咪royal級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5acb0c2558d28a2175d4553018e7b56d850a12","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落鹽抽水唔好咩，冇水先肉味濃喎同 dry aged 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下分析下<br />\n<br />\nDry aged 肉味濃既原因係 enzymatic, bacterial action, 脂肪 oxidation 等等既過程產生左 beefy or 好似芝士咁既味。<br />\n<br />\n另外肉入面既enzyme 會breakdown 左肉既組織，令肉食落去淋d。<br />\n<br />\n落鹽抽水就少左上面兩個效果。</blockquote><br />\n你啱Dry aged 唔止淨係抽水，不過抽水本身應該冇壞，尤其塊扒cheap</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBreakdown 肌肉組織仲可以令煎既時候水份流失少d。<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 鹽都可以breakdown 肌肉組織，不過慢慢進行，所以如果落完鹽等返一個鐘先煎又唔同情況。"},{"pid":"7318480c625206f214b721c4a89b2feffb193493","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊牛扒係咪royal級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我未識咩係royal 級，不過以我比既價錢睇應該唔係😂<br />\n片入面既扒全部都係大約$150 左右"},{"pid":"4a0f566cd5a3f16c44c813d33b1e650935441730","tid":482982,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舊牛扒係咪royal級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我未識咩係royal 級，不過以我比既價錢睇應該唔係😂<br />\n片入面既扒全部都係大約$150 左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nroyal級都唔識....學人係飲食台撈"},{"pid":"1155a2108443cdea4a22310d9b8a038b67a87adb","tid":482982,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"有冇試過用姆指掂食指，中指，無名指，尾指，然後用姆指厚肉果部分觸感呢個方法判斷"},{"pid":"2be6a65cc89ec0f89dc4f93bd2b0cc8d62f174a1","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>舊牛扒係咪royal級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我未識咩係royal 級，不過以我比既價錢睇應該唔係😂<br />\n片入面既扒全部都係大約$150 左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nroyal級都唔識....學人係飲食台撈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水密桃？"},{"pid":"2d7ac2b2afc8c19c8785b81f35bcc81f2d43eec1","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過用姆指掂食指，中指，無名指，尾指，然後用姆指厚肉果部分觸感呢個方法判斷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原理應該係一樣，<br />\n不過我自己就咁撳，記住個feel 就算"},{"pid":"fadf25eb7bd5b8efba2bbe4b0184ab4a51523af9","tid":482982,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>舊牛扒係咪royal級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我未識咩係royal 級，不過以我比既價錢睇應該唔係😂<br />\n片入面既扒全部都係大約$150 左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nroyal級都唔識....學人係飲食台撈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水密桃？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀識人先買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f589f43c9997e47c0307fdbc58e91930f0d130b1","tid":482982,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"點睇reverse searing? 我見上網都幾多人推介。"},{"pid":"5612e599332bf7739f468a075630a7d7db8ff593","tid":482982,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"個煎pan都要royal級"},{"pid":"79c96e7b11ed973a3b59a44cd5261241f3eaf1ea","tid":482982,"uid":77829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16c07ef1ee8466232a75361f2c36ac1c1d2d72d","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真"},{"pid":"3be9491e0c8e21ff324a7ddfdeac79c5e7322295","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇reverse searing? 我見上網都幾多人推介。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都聽過，聽過好似好合理。<br />\n如無意外聽日會試黎焗塊大d 既肉"},{"pid":"04365582bfb65949658a3c2be32c907ec21f4654","tid":482982,"uid":77829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但買黎淨係煎扒又好把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保養又麻煩<br />\n我仲係用緊隻特福pan ja，貪方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265ec16b11feb3b54c09469b02b642127d5801dd","tid":482982,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg&h=32f89a52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg&h=769ec176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰左 點解可以咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b36323e6d84c0575bf805b6266f36f268200a7","tid":482982,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg&h=32f89a52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg&h=769ec176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰左 點解可以咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塊扒太薄啦.... 茶餐廳級數既扒邊有得搞ga"},{"pid":"4db429102ee4a7520f923e9766c0e7f6d84f2d10","tid":482982,"uid":36100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但買黎淨係煎扒又好把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保養又麻煩<br />\n我仲係用緊隻特福pan ja，貪方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有一隻grill pan一隻平底，保養係堅麻煩<br />\n但當你養好隻鑊，cast iron煎嘢係無撚敵嘅<br />\n唔好講扒，煎隻蛋都好食好多<br />\n掉咗隻tefal佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ea8101da242634c1b60283a3f06dca58b8098b","tid":482982,"uid":77829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg&h=32f89a52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg&h=769ec176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰左 點解可以咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塊扒太薄啦.... 茶餐廳級數既扒邊有得搞ga</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 你塊扒薄到紙皮咁，不如切片打邊爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be7598bde8b241c81e9783b4e45fc8af8303909","tid":482982,"uid":77829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但買黎淨係煎扒又好把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保養又麻煩<br />\n我仲係用緊隻特福pan ja，貪方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有一隻grill pan一隻平底，保養係堅麻煩<br />\n但當你養好隻鑊，cast iron煎嘢係無撚敵嘅<br />\n唔好講扒，煎隻蛋都好食好多<br />\n掉咗隻tefal佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用邊隻，有無推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg&h=a3bc19ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前煎左塊 dry age ，真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e659ecc1c126fafd3d9910450982c6ee03ed7479","tid":482982,"uid":36100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但買黎淨係煎扒又好把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保養又麻煩<br />\n我仲係用緊隻特福pan ja，貪方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有一隻grill pan一隻平底，保養係堅麻煩<br />\n但當你養好隻鑊，cast iron煎嘢係無撚敵嘅<br />\n唔好講扒，煎隻蛋都好食好多<br />\n掉咗隻tefal佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用邊隻，有無推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg&h=a3bc19ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前煎左塊 dry age ，真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlodge，平底好用過grill<br />\n當玩到佢煎到荷包蛋嘅時候<br />\n你隻鑊就開光完成<br />\n不過火候控制要由頭適應過<br />\n因為熱得好慢，但夠熱之後就要閂細個火<br />\n如果唔係會overheat"},{"pid":"526c6648aceba22fa8a2b05ee30f1adf8f746034","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家用開咩pan 煎？<br />\n成日想買返隻生鐵pan 返去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想買隻cast iron 煎野，理論下個表應該係最好，想試下真唔真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但買黎淨係煎扒又好把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保養又麻煩<br />\n我仲係用緊隻特福pan ja，貪方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有一隻grill pan一隻平底，保養係堅麻煩<br />\n但當你養好隻鑊，cast iron煎嘢係無撚敵嘅<br />\n唔好講扒，煎隻蛋都好食好多<br />\n掉咗隻tefal佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用邊隻，有無推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F225401_08bb54335dd08cb32761ebd4036be7d9.jpg&h=a3bc19ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前煎左塊 dry age ，真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚野👏🏻"},{"pid":"b94ad464cc8231f2b8c526ac1212a808f44bf4bf","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222728_3b2e493bf2088cc303c0931a6f69a535.jpg&h=32f89a52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F222735_0ff130229a381269d89851db6f0abae6.jpg&h=769ec176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰左 點解可以咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薄到咁係有d 難度"},{"pid":"fed32421f0ea353dbe2a7196790b1ad0fa67412b","tid":482982,"uid":131963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"我用debuyer 深炒鑊，平時用黎炒菜，過時過節用黎煎牛扒一流.  缺點係要養鑊同好貴重...."},{"pid":"ec0cc3ec55305654f953f2ac3d45e7ddc487b012","tid":482982,"uid":30272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"倫敦邊度買肉？"},{"pid":"29b9bfc388ce58851ad5755103bf68fd0ff95a3a","tid":482982,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"慢煮棒加火槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec789434d766ff5b7b8c6bb82c47a7770978494","tid":482982,"uid":68044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T21:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慢煮棒加火槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個無得輸，有冇啲勁既火槍介紹"},{"pid":"e5434b1c5aa429bf14